{"tid":957912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯高冷美少女日本爆紅美如畫中人，仙氣十足","createTime":"2018-12-27T11:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T11:23:27.000Z","uid":212399,"like":77,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"216a9bdad63058a8e9e7bc36d1a1b51529942445","tid":957912,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"講道理，日本美女的質量還是很不錯的，哪怕有點先天不足，在島國&ldquo;化妝邪術&rdquo;的幫助下，也能秒變清純美少女。然而最近，一位俄羅斯的小姐姐突然就在日本火了，不少阿宅大讚她仙氣十足，彷彿是從油畫中走出的人。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/483/w600h683/20180717/fPul-hfkffam3782634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F483%2Fw600h683%2F20180717%2FfPul-hfkffam3782634.jpg&h=a7f1cd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本推友@margaret_yw在推特上分享了幾張俄羅斯小姐姐的照片，大贊照片中的她美如畫，顏值直擊心扉，這樣美麗的小姐姐自然也打動了很多網友，幾天就收穫了近6萬個點贊，還因此上了日推的熱榜。<br />\n據網友爆料，照片中的小姐姐名叫Milana Angelova，雖然有INS、臉書等社交賬號，不過基本已經沒有在更新，這樣仙女一樣的小姐姐你喜歡嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/94f10c47e3ea9d59b5f4aaf6ccb4c430.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2F94f10c47e3ea9d59b5f4aaf6ccb4c430.jpeg&h=92aba4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/be87ccf553a30e5bfcd954174133d24b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2Fbe87ccf553a30e5bfcd954174133d24b.jpeg&h=9916e9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/41/91/q5iUoKSXkqCXp6SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F41%2F91%2Fq5iUoKSXkqCXp6SY.jpg&h=057cef68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://loeildelaphotographie.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/misae_angel_02-x540q100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Floeildelaphotographie.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Fmisae_angel_02-x540q100.jpg&h=e7a33cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn